\id PHM 2011-04-02 SIL-BFB Buamu-Ouarkoye 
\h Filemɔn 
\toc1 Ho vũahṹ na ó o Poole túara nɔn o Filemɔn yi 
\toc2 Filemɔn 
\toc3 PHM 
\mt2 Ho vũahṹ na ó o Poole túara nɔn o 
\mt1 Filemɔn 
\mt2 yi 
\is1 Vũahṹ túaró ɲúhṹ 
\ip Ho vũahṹ na kà lé o Poole túara ho á nɔn o Filemɔn yi. O Filemɔn lé o Poole ɓàn bɔ̃́nlo. O fù lé o nùpue na bìo ɲúhṹ wi ɓa nùpua cɔ̃́n làa sòobɛ́ɛ, á lé ho Koloosi kèrètĩ́ɛwa kuure nì-kéní. O Filemɔn wobá-nìi ɓúi fù wi á lùwa ò o día a. O yèni ɓa le Onɛziimu. 
\ip Ho vũahṹ mu yi ó o Poole tɛ̀ɛnía o Filemɔn làa bìa làa wo páanía wi yi (1-3). O Poole dó le Dónbeenì bárákà o Filemɔn sĩidéró o Yeesu *Krista yi bìo yi, làa bìo ó o wa lè mín zàwa lè mín hĩ́nni kèrètĩ́ɛwa bìo yi (4-7). 
\ip Bìo ó o Onɛziimu wà día mí ɲúhṹso, ó o fò mín là a Poole ká wón wi ho kàsó yi, ó o Poole mu wó ó o tà a Yeesu bìo, á lé o kèrètĩ́ɛ. Bìo mu wó kà, ó o Poole le o bĩní yèrèmá va mí ɲúhṹso Filemɔn cɔ̃́n. Lé bṹn te bìo ó o túara ho vũahṹ nɔn o Filemɔn mu yi, á fìora a le ká a Onɛziimu bĩnía ɓuara a cɔ̃́n, ò o tà sɛ́n bìo ó o wó ɓúenɓúen día à na a yi, à ɓua a sese bìo ó o wã́a lé ɓàn za mu kèrètĩ́ɛmu dã́ní yi bìo yi (8-22). 
\c 1  
\s1 Le tɛ̀ɛníi 
\p  
\v 1 Mu lé ĩnɛ́n Poole, yìa wi ho kàsó yi o Yeesu *Krista tonló sáró bìo yi, lé mi wee túa ho vũahṹ na kà á na ũnɛ́n Filemɔn yi. O Timɔtee na lé wàn za, wón làa mi páanía wee tɛ̀ɛní foǹ, ũnɛ́n na làa wɛn páanía wee sá, na wa wa làa sòobɛ́ɛ.  
\v 2 Wa mún wee tɛ̀ɛní wàn hĩ́nló Apia yi, là a Aasiipu, wón mún làa wɛn páanía wee lá le lònbee lè mí sìíwà. Ɓa kèrètĩ́ɛwa kuure na wee kúee mín wán ũ zĩi á wa mún wee tɛ̀ɛní yi.  
\v 3 Le wàn Maá Dónbeenì là a Ɲúhṹso Yeesu *Krista à wé mí sãamu làa mia, à na ho hɛ́ɛrà mia. 
\s1 O Poole sĩi wan o Filemɔn bìo yi 
\p  
\v 4 Hen ká ĩ sansan wee fìo le Dónbeenì yi, à ĩ dé le bárákà ũ bìo yi.  
\v 5 Lé bìo á ũ sĩidéró o Yeesu *Krista yi á ĩ wee ɲí bìo, á mún wee ɲí bìo fo wa làa bìa ɓúenɓúen na bìo sã̀ le Dónbeenì yi.  
\v 6 Ĩ wee fìo le bìa dó mi sĩa o Krista yi làa fo páaní à pànká wíoka kɛń á wíoka zũń mu bè-tentewà ɓúenɓúen, bìo le Dónbeenì wee wé làa wɛn wa páaníló là a Krista bìo yi.  
\v 7 Lé bìo á bìo fo wa lè wàn zàwa lè wàn hĩ́nni á ĩ ɲá, á ĩ sĩi ɓɛ̀ntĩ́n wan, á sĩi hã̀ làa sòobɛ́ɛ mu bìo yi. Mu bon, bìa bìo sã̀ le Dónbeenì yi á fo hĩ̀ína sĩa. 
\s1 O Poole wee fìo o Filemɔn o Onɛziimu dã́ní yi 
\p  
\v 8-9 Lé bṹn te bìo á ĩ wee fìoráa fo le ũ wé bìo fo ko à ũ wé. Wa páaníló là a *Krista bìo yi, á ĩ lá dà à na le ɲii á à bío le ũ wé mu. Ɛ̀ɛ ká ĩ màhã́ pá à fìo fo bìo wa wa làa mín bìo yi. Àwa, á ĩnɛ́n nì-kĩ́nle Poole, yìa wi ho kàsó yi o Yeesu Krista tonló sáró bìo yi á pá wee fìo fo bìo wa wa làa mín bìo yi,  
\v 10 le ũ sábéré à ũ wé bìo á ĩ ì bío ò na foǹ o Onɛziimu dã́ní yi, wón na á ĩ wó ó o lé ĩ za mu kèrètĩ́ɛmu dã́ní yi ho kàsó yi.  
\v 11 O bìo ɲúhṹ lá mía ũ cɔ̃́n bṹn bon, ɛ̀ɛ ká hã laà na kà wán á ĩnɛ́n làa fo ó o bìo ɲúhṹ wã́a wi cɔ̃́n.\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Onɛziimu: Le yèni mu kúará le ‹mu ɲúhṹ wi›.\f* 
\p  
\v 12 Àwa, á ĩ wã́a à bío le o Onɛziimu mu bĩní ɓuen ũ cɔ̃́n, o bìo ɓɛ̀ntĩ́n here miì làa sòobɛ́ɛ.  
\v 13 Bìo á ĩ wi ho kàsó yi le bín-tente bìo yi, á ĩ yàá lá wi à ĩ día wo ĩ nìsã́ní, ò o wé séení mi ũ lahó yi.  
\v 14 Ɛ̀ɛ ká ĩ màhã́ yí wi à ĩ wé bìo ɓúi o dã́ní yi ká ĩ làa fo yí ɲá mín yi. Lé bìo á ĩ yí wi à mu tentemu na fo ò wé á à na miì à wé lè ĩ wee kĩ̀kã́ foǹ lè mu wéró, ká mu lé ũnɛ́n ũ bɛɛre yi. 
\p  
\v 15 Ɲún-sĩ á le Dónbeenì yàá wó ó o Onɛziimu khɛ̀ra làa fo ho pɔ̃̀n-za dɛ̀ɛ yi, bèra a na ká a bĩnía ɓuara ũ cɔ̃́n, à mi wã́a páaní kɛɛní fɛ́ɛɛ.  
\v 16 Hã laà na kà wán ó o yínɔń wobá-nìi mí dòn, o bìo ɲúhṹ wi po bṹn. O wã́a lé mìn za kèrètĩ́ɛ, á fo ko à ũ wíoka wań wo làa sòobɛ́ɛ. O lé wàn za kèrètĩ́ɛ na á ĩ ɓɛ̀ntĩ́n wa làa sòobɛ́ɛ. Á ĩ mún láa mu yi le fo ò wíoka à wań wo á yàá a poń ĩnɛ́n, bìo ó o bìo sã̀ foǹ bìo yi, làa bìo mi páanía là a Ɲúhṹso bìo yi. 
\p  
\v 17 Àwa, ká fo zũ le warɛ́n lé ɓa bɔ̃́nlowà binbirí, ká a bĩnía ɓuara ũ cɔ̃́n, à ũ ɓua a sese, à kɛń lè lé ĩnɛ́n ĩ bɛɛre.  
\v 18 Ká a wó khon làa fo bìo ɓúi yi, tàá ká a ko ò o wĩ́ bìo ɓúi foǹ síi, à ũ ɲì mu ĩnɛ́n ɲúhṹ yi.  
\v 19 Hã ɲi-cúa na á ĩ wee túa lè ĩ nín-bia lé hĩ̀a kà: «Ĩnɛ́n Poole á à wĩ́ ũ kení na wi o yi». Ĩ yí máa bío le fo ko à ũ wĩ́ bìo ɓúi miì, ká fo màhã́ ko à ũ zũń lé ĩnɛ́n lé yìa zéenía o Yeesu bìo làa fo á fo yúráa le mukãnì binbirì.  
\v 20 Àwa, wàn za Filemɔn, á ĩ wee fìo fo o Ɲúhṹso yèni yi le ũ wé bìo á ĩ wee fìo fo le ũ wé. Wa páaníló là a *Krista bìo yi, ũ yí día le ĩ yilera lùnka mu bìo yi. 
\p  
\v 21 Ĩ láa mu yi le bìo á ĩ túara ho vũahṹ yi le ũ wé á fo ò wé kɛ̃́nkɛ̃́n. Ĩ yàá zũ le fo ò wé yòó puuní bìo á ĩ le ũ wé yi.  
\v 22 Mún cà le zĩi ɓúi ká làa mi. Ho fìoró na mi wee wé ĩ bìo yi, á ĩ láa mu yi le hen làa cĩ́inú ká ĩ yí ĩten ɓueé ɓúɛɛkí mia. 
\s1 Le mɔ́ndɛ́n tɛ̀ɛníi 
\p  
\v 23 O Epafaraasi na làa mi páanía wi ho kàsó yi o Yeesu *Krista tonló sáró bìo yi wee tɛ̀ɛní foǹ.  
\v 24 O Maaki, là a Arisitaaki, là a Demaasi, là a Luki, bán ɓúenɓúen na làa wɛn páanía wee sá ho tonló dà-kéní á mún wee tɛ̀ɛní foǹ. 
\p  
\v 25 Le wa Ɲúhṹso Yeesu *Krista à wé mí sãamu làa mia.